Hello everyone,

As you might already know, IITM has an immense international outreach (NIRF
#1), and there are a wide variety of international opportunities that
IITM's students can avail.
After a successful fundae session for undergraduate students, we now
present to you:


INTERNATIONAL OPPORTUNITIES FUNDAE SESSIONFOR POSTGRADUATE STUDENTS
Date: Friday, 23rd September
Venue: IC&SR Auditorium
Time: 7:00 pm 

Questions to be addressed for Exchange programs

    Why an exchange programme?  Pros and Cons.
    Currently available opportunities  Universities & scholarship/funding
    What is the best time to go for an exchange?
    What is the procedure for applying, and what all do you need? 
   CV/Resume, SoPs, Recos etc.
    Post selection process, and administrative procedures
    Funding application procedure and other relevant issues

In case you have any specific questions to ask, please fill the form
